message.body: Oh my goodness Sheridan. I've had a very long day. Dads car broke down last night so we couldn't leave for nyc until this morning in a rental car. And then we dropped the little puppy off at kk's and he ran away from kelly, so we came back to look for him and couldn't find him:( now we're in Pennsylvania and still have 3 hours to go, and the sick puppy is nowhere to be found. So much stress.

Oh gosh, I really hope they find him, and I'm so sorry to hear about the car. I love you dearly and everything will be okay. You are almost back to classes and your schduele of life. Plus you have tons of awesome people hear for you
❤️❤️❤️ love you so much Sheridan!!! Tell me about Minnesota! How's everything there?
Everything is alright, I've been dealing with some emotions and being scared. I'm still waiting to hear back from the u of m, and I hurt my back so ehh. But i think everything is getting better

You're so brave, dear! You've got nothing to worry about- you're strong and beautiful and can make it through anything! And a long hot shower might not fix your back, but I guarantee you'll feel better
